text: Nay Myo Aung (born 19 July 1986) is an archer from Myanmar. Myo Aung competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Nay Myo AungNay MYO AUNG == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese archers Category:Olympians for Myanmar
